original: Bought late last night, virtually untouched.  I found it on my pillow this morning - must have passed out after one bite.  Hot sauce, extra cheese.  Looks like I threw some mayo on there as well.  Cheap lunch for somebody.  Just give me a couple of dollars so I can buy myself an eye-opener.
translated: 昨晚买的，几乎全新。今早在枕头上找到的，多半是咬了一口就昏倒了。加辣，多加奶酪，好像还放了蛋黄酱。很划算的午餐选择。给我点钱买杯酒喝就行。
